parameters.name: SAMPLE TIME
parameters.description:
Spacecraft event time at which the spacecraft sampled the magnetometer  
      instrument memory in order to generate the packetized data. Time is     
      given in PDS format: yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sss. The individual elements   
      of the time field can be read using the format (i4,4(1x,i2),1x,f6.3)    
      yr, mon, day, hr, min, sec.

parameters.name: SPACECRAFT CLOCK
parameters.description: Spacecraft clock counter in the form RIM:mod91:mod10:mod8.

parameters.name: BX_SC
parameters.description:
Bx field component in the despun spacecraft coordinate system (roughly  
      anti-Earthward).

parameters.name: BY_SC
parameters.description:
By field component in the despun spacecraft coordinate system           
      (southward).

parameters.name: BZ_SC
parameters.description:
Bz field component in the despun spacecraft coordinate system           
      (dawnward).

parameters.name: B-FIELD MAGNITUDE
parameters.description: Magnitude of the average B-field components.

parameters.name: ROTOR TWIST
parameters.description: Rotor twist (spin phase) angle, EME-50 coordinates.

parameters.name: ROTOR SPIN
parameters.description: Rotor spin phase angle, ECL-50 coordinates.
